; Return to 2,0 wash and park
G1 Z5 F500;         ; Raise brush to safe height
G0 X2 Y0 F1000;     ; Return to cleaning position
G1 Z0 F500;         ; Lower brush for cleaning
G1 Z2 F500;         ; Raise brush slightly
G1 X22 Y0 F500;     ; Move across cleaning area
G1 Z5 F500;         ; Raise brush to safe height
G0 X2 Y0 F1000;     ; Return to wash position
G1 Z0 F500;         ; Lower brush for cleaning
G1 Z2 F500;         ; Raise brush slightly
G1 X22 Y0 F500;     ; Move across cleaning area
G1 Z5 F500;         ; Raise brush completely
G0 X20 Y110 Z10 F500;; Move to parking position with Z at safe height
M2;                 ; End program
